  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nThe extended debug logger has a property `show_debug2` which is supposed to return `False` unless the log will be emitted to a file or stderr. At some point, it started returning `True` in all cases (at least when run in Trinity).\r\n\r\nThis is causing more than a 2x slowdown in import speed.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\n:man_shrugging: \r\n",
